1,'2014-02-07 16:22:06','2014-02-07 16:22:06','<h3><span style=\"color: #8a359c;\">Get Paid to Do What You Love</span></h3>\r\n<em>Sonic Escape</em> works with both performers and non-performers to:\r\n\r\n1. Identify one\'s interests, skills &amp; creative abilities\r\n2. Come up with an idea\r\n3. Create a plan to transform the idea from concept into reality by leveraging one\'s capabilities\r\n\r\n<em>Sonic Escape’s</em> founders turned a love of performing, composing, traveling and meeting new people into a full-time, self-managed career; now it’s YOUR turn to have your dreams define your everyday routine!\r\n<a href=\"http://www.sonicescapemusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Sonic-Escape-Workshops.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Click for more workshop options</a>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #8a359c;\">5-Day Residency</span></h3>\r\n<em>Sonic Escape</em> presents a 5-day residency with workshops and masterclasses on chamber music playing, improvisation, collaboration, research and presentation.  The activities culminate in a concert for the local community by <em>Sonic Escape</em> and residency participants!  <a href=\"http://www.sonicescapemusic.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Sonic-Escape-Residency-Project.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Click for example of past residency project</a>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #8a359c;\">Concert and a Hike</span></h3>\r\n<em>Sonic Escape</em> is deeply committed to developing audiences in partnership with presenters.  One initiative currently under way - <em>Concert and a Hike</em> - involves group hikes &amp; flash performances at popular gathering places leading up to the main concert.  In cooperation with your marketing team, <em>Sonic Escape</em> will implement creative strategies to bring audiences in!','Workshops/Outreach','','publish','closed','open','','workshopsoutreach','','','2014-02-08 12:41:51','2014-02-08 12:41:51','',45,'http://www.sonicescapemusic.com/?page_id=676',0,'page','',0),(677,1,'2014-02-07 16:22:06','2014-02-07 16: